Title: The Dynamic Language Runtime, IronRuby and IronPython with Jimmy Schementi
Description: Scott sits down with Jimmy Schementi to find out what's the scoop with the DLR. Is it baked? What do I need to do to get started? What's the status of IronRuby - is it done? Will IronPython be a first class language or is it already? All these questions and more will be answered.
